<!DOCTYPE html><html><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><title>Anualidad Vencida</title><link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/styles.css"><link rel="icon" href="/img/Icon.ico"></head><body>@include('pages.partials.header')<main class="container"><h2 class="calc-title">Anualidad Vencida</h2><p class="calc-subtitle">Pagos iguales al final de cada periodo. Calcula su valor presente y valor futuro.</p><div class="formula">VP = A · [1 - (1 + i)⁻ⁿ] / i</div><section class="panel-grid"><div class="card"><div class="grid-2"><div class="field"><label>Cuota / pago (A)</label><div class="input-wrap"><input id="A" type="number"><span>$</span></div></div><div class="field"><label>Tasa por periodo (i)</label><div class="input-wrap"><input id="iA" type="number"><span>%</span></div></div><div class="field"><label>Número de periodos (n)</label><input id="nA" type="number"></div></div><div class="mt"><button id="calc-av">Calcular</button></div></div><div class="card result-card"><div><div>Ingresa los datos y presiona Calcular para ver el resultado.</div><div id="result" class="result-value"></div></div></div></section></main>@include('pages.partials.footer')<script src="/js/calculadora.js"></script></body></html>
